{"tid":1343871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"從今日開始，人人都可以做的事 - 全民急救員計劃","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:50:23.000Z","uid":90260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1393e8499884c957c7072e611032759f55dcad","tid":1343871,"uid":90260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:44:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">A. 報考急救課程</span><br />\n懂急救的好處大家都知道<br />\n今次好彩死的不是自己人，但隱疾有機會隱藏於每人之中，<span style=\"color: red;\">及時且正確的CPR可以讓你身邊的人逃出鬼門關</span><br />\n即報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSt. John <a href=\"https://ereg.stjohn.org.hk/schedule/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fereg.stjohn.org.hk%2Fschedule%2Findex.html&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=dd9e222d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ereg.stjohn.org.hk/schedule/index.html</a><br />\n紅十字 <a href=\"https://training.redcross.org.hk/tms/zh-HK/courseSearch.jspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftraining.redcross.org.hk%2Ftms%2Fzh-HK%2FcourseSearch.jspx&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=9bd83271\" target=\"_blank\">https://training.redcross.org.hk/tms/zh-HK/courseSearch.jspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">B. 隨身攜帶急救包</span><br />\n如果你出街喜歡帶大背囊，可考慮長駐一個急救包，你可以按背囊的容量選擇急救包，不需要太大。而且不一定需要那個紅噹噹的袋，搵一個乾淨的收納袋就可以。<br />\n基本配備為 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">膠手套，生理鹽水，消毒酒精，紗布，敷料，繃帶</span><br />\n紅十字<a href=\"https://rcshop.redcross.org.hk/index.php?route=product/category&amp;path=63_90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frcshop.redcross.org.hk%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dproduct%2Fcategory%26path%3D63_90&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=adad4af8\" target=\"_blank\">https://rcshop.redcross.org.hk/index.php?route=product/category&amp;path=63_90</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">亦於各行山用品店，網上店鋪有售，在此並不一一詳列</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即使你不諳急救知識，亦可以在危急時候提供物資協助</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">(P.S.記得按時檢查藥水/鹽水/敷料有效期，定時更換)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KP6MUCK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKP6MUCK.png&h=05352cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>於現場環境安全下，保護你身邊的人。<br />\n祝各位好人<span style=\"color: red;\">一生平安</span>，你的知識永遠派不上用場。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976739cd572a18dbf5f6ecb736da4b5a25537c3b","tid":1343871,"uid":90260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:50:33.000Z","msg":"推佢老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef02eaf894bb7d77bdb0785069fec10f681b26fa","tid":1343871,"uid":120906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:53:35.000Z","msg":"全民打手會唔會實際d，得醫療兵冇陸戰隊有咩用？"},{"pid":"d690112a809c4466b9e415900e542f7ac0419675","tid":1343871,"uid":268894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}